***NEW STORIES OUT EVERY WEEK DAY***

WELCOME TO HELLMONTH: A NEW TAP ORIGINAL SERIES
Supernatural forces have descended on Boston in what will be known as the 'month of hell'. A month-long series of stories where citizens try to survive the demonic forces that plague the city. New story will be released every weekday.

Keep your app up to date with the latest version for more surprise and fright during Halloween month!

Our thrilling story, Live Police Stop, puts you in the driver’s seat—literally—as Chloe is unfairly pulled over. Want to play matchmaker? In Secret Prince, Jax’s future is in your hands as you make decisions for her that ultimately determine how her love story will end. Will she end up with Nick? That’s up to you.
